## 🚀 사용 예제

### 1. 컨테이너 배포 파이프라인
```javascript
import { ContainerOrchestrator } from './container-orchestrator.js';

const orchestrator = new ContainerOrchestrator();

const result = orchestrator.deployApplication('quantum-app', {
  version: '2.0',
  dockerfile: 'Dockerfile',
  context: './src',
  registry: 'registry.gogs.dclub.kr',
  replicas: 3,
  port: 8080,
  serviceType: 'LoadBalancer'
});

console.log(`Deployment: ${result.application}`);
console.log(`Service: ${result.service}`);
```

### 2. 자동 스케일링
```javascript
import { ScaleManager } from './auto-scaler.js';

const manager = new ScaleManager();
manager.registerDeployment('quantum-ml', 3);

// 자동 스케일링 실행
const result = manager.runAutoScaling('quantum-ml', 75, 80, 500);

console.log(`Scaled: ${result.scaled}`);
console.log(`New replicas: ${result.newReplicas}`);
console.log(`Reason: ${result.reason}`);

// 부하 예측
const prediction = manager.predictScale('quantum-ml', {
  cpuPercentage: 90,
  memoryPercentage: 85
});

console.log(`Predicted: ${prediction.predictedReplicas} replicas`);
```

### 3. SLA 모니터링
```javascript
import { SLAMonitor } from './sla-monitor.js';

const monitor = new SLAMonitor(99.9);

// 메트릭 기록
monitor.recordMetric(true, 150, true);   // healthy, 150ms, success
monitor.recordMetric(true, 180, true);   // healthy, 180ms, success
monitor.recordMetric(true, 250, false);  // healthy, 250ms, failed

// SLA 리포트
const report = monitor.generateReport();

console.log(`Availability: ${report.availability.availability}`);
console.log(`Error Rate: ${report.errorRate.errorRate}`);
console.log(`Latency P95: ${report.responseTime.p95}ms`);
console.log(`Status: ${report.summary.allTargetsMet ? 'PASSING' : 'FAILING'}`);
```

### 4. 로그 수집 및 분석
```javascript
import { LogAggregationSystem } from './log-aggregator.js';

const aggregator = new LogAggregationSystem();

// 로그 수집
const sourceLogs = [
  { source: 'api', level: 'INFO', message: 'Request received' },
  { source: 'api', level: 'ERROR', message: 'Database failed' },
  { source: 'worker', level: 'WARN', message: 'Queue backup' }
];

aggregator.ingestLogs(sourceLogs);

// 로그 검색
const searchResult = aggregator.searchLogs({
  source: 'api',
  level: 'ERROR'
});

console.log(`Found ${searchResult.matchCount} error logs`);

// 분석 리포트
const report = aggregator.generateAnalysisReport(
  Date.now() - 3600000,  // 1시간 전
  Date.now()
);

console.log(`Error rate: ${report.errorRate}`);
console.log(`Top sources: ${JSON.stringify(report.topSources)}`);
```

